- Information about the orders has been structured
- The price is displayed with breakdown by methods of payment
- Orders with the increased price are marked
- Possibility to view the order route on the map has been added
- Extras to the orders now have icons
- Block with a comment to the order and information about the client is now separate
- Interaction with third-party navigation applications has been improved
- New orders are highlighted in colour

- Added "auto assignment" button to all tabs;
- Added the countdown for order assignment confirmation;
- Added the ability to edit waypoints;
- Added the "Stop application" button on the 5th tab;
- Added a panel with the full information of the order to the "Map" tab;
- Added a panel with action buttons to the "Map" tab;
- Added a real-time updating of the arrival time countdown to order;
- Added "feedback";
